<p><b>How to read and meditate on God's word?</b> Allow enough time for a passage of several verses. After choosing a passage of Scripture, read it slowly two or three times. Then focus on the passage, phrase by phrase, considering its message and how it speaks to your life. Continue this practice for several days.</p>
